installation:
=============

Add to python path, and then add to INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py
run "manage.py syncdb"

add the following to your urls.py file:

(r'^forum/', include('forum_new_style', namespace='forum'

Adding forums:
==============

Go to the admin (http://localhost:8000/admin) and click on Forums.

Add the name of the forums you want, plus an aditional description.




The philospphy of this project:
===============================

Users are free to delete whatever content that post, even if it's posted anonymously
Anonymous posting should be easy and encouraged
Administrator personas should be used in moderation (no pun intended)
